title.narrative: Support to Water Management in the SADC/Zambezi Region

description.narrative: The Danish support to water management in the SADC/Zambezi Region 2012-2016 will improve water resources development and management in Southern Africa with a specific focus on the Zambezi river basin, the largest river basin in Southern Africa.
